        <p>Stroke is a medical emergency. Prompt diagnosis and treatment at Brain stroke hospitals in secunderabad reduces the brain damage and other complications. A stroke occurs when a blood vessel breaks and bleedsor when there's a blockage in the blood supply to the brain. The rupture or blockage reduces the blood and oxygen supply to the brain tissues.</p>
        <h3 class="subheader">There are 3 main types of strokes:</h3>
        <ul style="position: relative;">
            <li><b>Ischemic stroke:</b> This is the most common type of stroke, making up 80-85% of all cases. In this type , blood clot occludes the blood and oxygen from reaching the brain tissue.</li>
            <li><b>Hemorrhagic stroke:</b> This happens when a blood vessel ruptures. These are coomly due to trauma or hypertension or structural lesions like aneurysms or arteriovenous malformations.</li>
            <li><b>Transient ischemic assault (TIA):</b>This occurs when blood flow to a part of the brain is reduced / cutoff for a brief time period. Normal blood flow resumes after a short period of time, and the symptoms resolve without treatment.</li>
        </ul>
